title: NEOS wins in Vienna (ELDR - European Liberal, Democratic and Reform Party)
text: ( Source : ELDR - European Liberal , Democratic and Reform Party ) Following a polarised election campaign for the city council of Vienna , regarded as regional parliamentary elections, ALDE Party member NEOS succeeded in entering the Parliament
